DOC.brief_summary: A randomized, open-labeled, oral dose, crossover design clinical trial to evaluate pharmacokinetics and safety between DWC20151 and DWC20152 in healthy male subjects.
DOC.brief_title: A Clinical Trial to Evaluate Pharmacokinetics and Safety Between DWC20151 and DWC20152
DOC.detailed_description: This study is to evaluate pharmacokinetics and safety between DWC20151 and DWC20152 in healthy male subjects. Study design is randomized, open-labeled, oral dose, crossover design. This study will conducted with 2 separated part (Part A, Part B).
DOC.criteria: Healthy male subjects (18~55 years) Who has allergy to investigational product
